2YzGzTRKJg">Tây các dạ - 西閣夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-L%E1%BB%85/Th%C3%A0nh-Th%C3%A1i-Qu%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%B5-xu%C3%A2n/poem-VitmhCD_-rxRLSyxCHD4CQ">Thành Thái Quý Tỵ xuân - 成泰癸巳春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-L%E1%BB%85/author-OUaOrdxXGI_1h3eak8TDHw">Cao Ngọc Lễ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-09/poem-CKmq1rVSIAAjJjl3zCPFXA">Thủ 09 - 首０９</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ge9IfP4qAzGhQhdEqnXX9g">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
